toyoPersona.description:
"Slicky was built with the most common  materials. Almost discardable, he was introduced as a substitute for The Collectors in the test of lethal traps in the Arena of Trials.

Now, with the Collectors next to them, they help run part of The Dome black market; many low tier parts can be found in their street markets as well as many other goods you can only find in Jakana."
toyoPersona.name: Slicky
